The paper discusses the validation of clustering algorithms, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions fuzzy adaptive resonance theory-based clustering methods, which fall under the category of neural networks and computational neuroscience (cs.NE). The use of cluster validity indices is also relevant to natural language processing and text mining (cs.CL) and signal processing (cs.SI).
